      "title": "Sri Lanka shares slip over 1-pct in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka shares slip over 1 percent in mid-day trade on Thursday (25) for the second day, Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index fell 1.24% or 111.55 points to 8,899.69 at 1140 hours.",
        "The most liquid index slipped 1.35 percent or 39.82 points to 2,904.68."
